{"tid":2288885,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[MOLA MOLA] 黃之鋒一家近日態度軟化","createTime":"2020-11-17T00:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T14:27:22.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e6831fe7f18da81af5151b755ed490e36494c8","tid":2288885,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"市場消息指，前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒家人持有的鴨脷洲海怡半島一單位，有指在市場上放盤數月後，終以980萬元賣出，<span class=\"red\">較銀行估值低逾一成</span>。本報正向黃之鋒求證，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：屋宇署9月批23份圖則 白建時道81號獲批建3層高住宅<br />\n區內地產代理透露，海怡半島13座一個極高層3房單位，屬頂樓對下一層的「鳳凰樓」，望樓景，實用面積633方呎，剛以980萬元沽出，呎價15,482元。據知，該單位在市場上已放盤數月，賣方原本叫價1,050萬元，直至<span class=\"red\">近日態度軟化</span>，累減70萬元終獲承接。參考滙豐銀行網上估值1,124萬元，<span class=\"red\">今次成交賣平144萬元或逾一成</span>。土地註冊處資料顯示，原業主為黃偉明，與黃之鋒父親同名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201116/MMMPXQA2XZEO5H2YE6JJIOE7RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201116%2FMMMPXQA2XZEO5H2YE6JJIOE7RI%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu7PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=553de394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201116%2FMMMPXQA2XZEO5H2YE6JJIOE7RI%2F&h=da5ea592\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201116/MMMPXQA2XZEO5H2YE6JJIOE7RI/</a>"},{"pid":"7b174d433658d41dc1a410acfe2eb53f6f8723d2","tid":2288885,"uid":57723,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:10:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬有潛質做 fake news media 記者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e1de8f3fa91a3f589cbf412a58f51601d4644e","tid":2288885,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b174d433658d41dc1a410acfe2eb53f6f8723d2","tid":2288885,"uid":57723,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:10:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬有潛質做 fake news media 記者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:13:51.000Z","msg":